{"about_the_game":"Primordial Pain is a brutally unforgiving, fast paced arena shooter with one key mechanic:<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/Header_Pain.png?t=1667248141\" /><br>Pain serves both as your health and as a multiplier for your damage output.<br>While playing you're constantly performing an elegant dance on the fine line of maximum power and certain death.<br>To defeat the primordial horrors that lurk in the darkness and overcome the pain you must perfect the dance.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/Gif_Pain.gif?t=1667248141\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/Header_Gameplay.png?t=1667248141\" /><br>Primordial Pain constrains you to a seemingly small arena, provides you with various different movement options and proceeds to through waves of enemies at you each requiring a different strategy to defeat.<br>You will have to experiment with every single mechanic at your disposal to discover optimal strategies or you will get overwhelmed by hordes of adversaries.<br>Survive long enough and great ancient beasts will reveal themselves.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/Gif_Dance.gif?t=1667248141\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2181000/extras/Header_Scoring.png?t=1667248141\" /><br>While playing you can either focus on surviving for as long as possible or to top your own highscore.<br>Whereas time constantly ticks up, your score depends on how quickly you can dispatch enemies as well as your method.<br>Playing in a stylish way will reward you with more points to be added to your score.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Behemoth","path":"https://cdn.akamai.s